{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act21side", "eventName": "敘拉古人", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IS-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "危如累卵", "storyInfo": "喬萬娜受襲倒地，食品安全部部長拜託拉維妮婭幫忙，能天使找上阿格尼爾，提出了困擾自己許久的問題。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g1_srcstreet", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#3"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯！", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特琳娜小姐......不，喬萬娜小姐，可能有危險！", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛才給她打了個電話，感覺很不好。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......拉普蘭德。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗨。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼事。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想要告訴你，你的那個老朋友，現在正在你們的據點附近，被自己家族的人團團圍住。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#2"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯，我們應該去幫喬萬娜小姐！", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#2"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的打算去嗎？", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不惜與羅塞蒂為敵都要離開這片土地。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卻又要為了她主動留在這座泥潭裡？", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想清楚了，德克薩斯。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在是你轉身離開的唯一機會。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空......", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯，你知道嗎。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然只是一點為了尋找你而發展的副業。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我發現，我逐漸喜歡上敘拉古的演藝氛圍了。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的人雖然也有那種傲慢，但比龍門那些充滿銅臭味的商人要好了太多。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能天使也總是喊著，要找到敘拉古最美味的披薩。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可頌......可頌的性格本來就挺隨遇而安的啦。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#4"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛才就想和你聊聊，或許可以等到大家都玩夠了再回龍門。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#4"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們總會回到龍門，而且是四個人一起。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#5"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，四個人一起。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#5"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_101_sora_1#5"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，不對，我剛才和喬萬娜小姐聊過了，我想請她也一起去龍門逛逛，所以應該是五個人。", "name": "空"}, "figure_art": "char_101_sora_1#5"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 6.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pistol", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 12.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunsingle", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunsingle", "volume": 0.9, "delay": 0.2, "channel": "z"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_skill_blacktimewand_shot", "volume": 0.9, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.9, "r": 0.8, "g": 0.8, "b": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.7, "channel": "z", "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巷子裡倒下了數人。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而喬萬娜的身上已經出現了不少傷口。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人，包括她自己，都知道，她絕無可能逃脫。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬萬娜，投降吧。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#7$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瓦拉赫，有酒嗎？", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......去車上拿一瓶。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_031"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "羅塞蒂家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_031"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......瓦拉赫，我是想過的，哥倫比亞的有些生意我們是不是做了會更好。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石武器，新型藥物，軍方的管道......", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想過，是不是有些機會我應該去把握住。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些官員的討好，甚至是哥倫比亞政府的橄欖枝。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我始終覺得，有些事應當適可而止。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#2$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是既得利益者，我們搶佔了太多的東西，我不會自稱善良，但至少，我們不能忘記，有些事是我們不能做的。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以說是原則，也可以說是一點無聊的堅持。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時代變了，喬萬娜。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的時代，需要新的準則。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一套老人們信奉的所謂道義，該被拋棄了。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使我們不做，也會有人去做，到時候，我們就會成為被拋棄的那一方。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說，看著哥倫比亞的其他家族染指那些東西，就是正確的嗎？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是你，你會怎麼做，瓦拉赫？", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#10$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會掌控那一切，無論是新的事物，還是舊的事物，都由我來支配。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而不是回到一片守舊的土地上，選擇對那些東西熟視無睹。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_031"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瓦拉赫，酒拿來了。", "name": "羅塞蒂家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_031"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，瓦拉赫，最後為我倒一杯。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$pourwater"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我的最愛。你早就準備好了，是嗎？", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來是想等你回來，作為慶祝的。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，從現在起，你就是羅塞蒂的首領了。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#9$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬萬娜。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_687_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動手。", "name": "喬萬娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_687_1#2$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#2$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knife"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銳器穿透身體的聲音在小巷中響起。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後迅速被雨聲淹沒。"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowsrun"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯知道，自己來晚了。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰鬥的痕跡遍佈小巷，血水在地上蔓延。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她順著血水的方向看去，一個熟悉的身影倒在地上。"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她心中一顫。"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬萬娜！", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g7_reception", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡，應該能讓我們好好聊一聊，法官小姐。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會成為你的幫兇。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫兇......你的用詞太激烈了。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#5$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你不應該先感謝我為你解圍嗎？", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#5$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算啦，就當是我自作多情吧。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們年輕人啊，優點是有衝勁，缺點呢，就是容易衝過頭。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，我也並沒有真正需要你幫我做的事。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是不想看到一個優秀的年輕人失敗在前進路上罷了。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你？不想看到？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來你因為卡拉奇的事對我有所誤解。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不認為自己有什麼誤解你的地方。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是更加在乎眼前的事物罷了。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“政府就像是灰廳中那張圓桌的桌布。”", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉維妮婭小姐，敘拉古人人都知道西西里夫人的這句感慨。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我想，知道這句感慨從何而來的人，恐怕寥寥無幾吧。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三十年前，有一群和你有些類似，天真地以為，自己可以讓敘拉古脫離家族掌控的青年。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，籠罩在敘拉古天上的陰雲是連綿的，他們無法找到支持他們的人。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，他們選擇了用利益籠絡數個家族，試圖去反抗那個......他們自以為能夠對抗的東西。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，他們的下場......沒有人知道。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人......知道？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想像一下這個場景吧，拉維妮婭小姐。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的父親是一名在市政府工作的書記員。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "某天，你正常地起床，洗漱，吃完早飯，你發現父親忘帶了東西，你的母親讓你去送給他。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時是雨季，你的心情也比較糟糕，因為你剛和你的父親吵了一架，但是你想，你也有不對的地方，去道歉就好了。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，當你走進市政大廳的時候，你感覺到一股寂靜。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平時這個時候，市政大廳是不可能如此安靜的。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，你看到各個辦公室門縫中，流出的潺潺血液。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這時候，你才注意到，大廳的地板上，到處都是血痕。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......！", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#4$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你發現，整個市政大廳的人都不見了。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更令你感到恐慌的是，你發現沒有人對這件事發表看法。無論你去問誰，甚至是你的母親，他們的態度都是一樣的，沉默。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像，那些消失的人從一開始就沒有存在過一樣。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過了一段時間，市政大廳裡又陸續開始出現了人，再過了一段時間，裡面又恢復了往日的熱鬧。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，你意識到，這一切就是這樣的。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是從那時起，西西里夫人的那句話，開始流傳開來。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“政府就像是灰廳中那張圓桌的桌布”，而桌布，自然是可以隨意更換的。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你經歷過這一切之後，你自然會明白——", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憤怒，憤怒當然存在，但憤怒過後呢？", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憤怒的過後是虛無。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像你現在這樣，你甚至不知道你應該向誰發洩滿腔的不忿。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是貝納爾多閣下？是貝洛內家族？還是西西里夫人？", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，都不是，他們都是這個秩序的一部分，而你，作為這份秩序的守門人，你比誰都清楚——", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是如此地不可撼動。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以呢，所以你想告訴我，我只能像你一樣，閉上雙眼，捂住耳朵，對正在發生的一切置若罔聞。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假裝自己在進行一種生活。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉維妮婭小姐，你甚至比我的女兒還要天真。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#4$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而作為一個過來人，我的建議和你來找我時一樣——無論你有怎樣的理想，首先，活下去。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#4$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算你真的急著去送死，也至少找到一個接班人。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#4$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "活著把一些想法傳遞下去，有時候，或許比慷慨赴死還要困難。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#4$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，過幾天我就要上任了，貝納爾多閣下為我安排了一場面向全市的演講。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不需要幫我做什麼，但或許，你可以替我照顧一下我的妻子和女兒。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，這應該沒有超出你的原則範圍。", "name": "盧比奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g3_srccourt", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？孩子，你不跟你的朋友一起離開嗎？", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......我有個比較個人的問題想要請教您。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#4$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "願聞其詳。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在學校時瞭解過一些您的事情，您當年和教宗閣下都是十分被看好的青年才俊。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而您卻在西西里夫人造訪拉特蘭後，義無反顧地跟隨西西里夫人離開了拉特蘭。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想知道，我為什麼跟著西西里離開拉特蘭？", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我好奇的是，您和西西里夫人關係一定很好吧？", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這要看你如何定義“很好”，若是要說瞭解，確實或許沒有人比我更瞭解西西里。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，我們的性格實際上大不相同。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少時至今日，對我來說，我更樂得在這樣的城市中躲避她帶給我的麻煩。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這也是關係好的一種體現吧？", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不否認。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您是怎麼跟西西里夫人相處了幾十年的？", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#8$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈！", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿格尼爾爺爺，我很認真的。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這真是個絕妙的問題，孩子。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠比你的朋友提出的問題要有趣。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但首先，我很好奇。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從你們剛才的描述來看，你和德克薩斯關係很好。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，我們是最好的搭檔~", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你並不懷疑你們的友情。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼——哦，我明白了，這個問題的來由。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "共感讓你對人毫無保留，但是，在與無法共感的人的相處過程中，你終究還是會產生懷疑。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，你害怕的不是遭到欺騙，而是這種懷疑本身。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你被報以真誠時，你對這種懷疑感到羞恥。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但同時，你又害怕，如果有一天這份懷疑成真，你將如何自處。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對，我就是這個意思！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#4$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，每一個離開了拉特蘭的薩科塔，都會遇到這樣的問題。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年，西西里旅居拉特蘭時，我負責了她的嚮導。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而實際上，我並不是如同傳聞中那樣，被西西里的想法所打動，而後跟隨她離開拉特蘭的。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時的西西里尚且年輕，她再怎麼天縱之才，也不可能在拉特蘭旅居一段時間，立刻想到了改變敘拉古的方法。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的想法稚嫩且不切實際，但於我來說，卻正好與我當時的一些想法不謀而合。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們為此日夜討論，爭執，直到最後，我才終於決定，跟隨她前往敘拉古，印證我與她的想法。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "討論，爭執。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而來到敘拉古之後，我們之間的爭執，也從未消失。實際上，我們對於敘拉古的看法，從未真正統一過。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這並不妨礙我們互相瞭解對方的想法。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，討論與爭執就是秘訣？", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#4$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，你覺得呢？", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得不是。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#8$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和德克薩斯很少認真討論一些什麼，只是不知道什麼時候開始，我們就成了好搭檔了。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聰明的孩子。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到最後，將我與西西里綁在一起的，並非理念，並非局勢，甚至可能並非情感。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而是歲月。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歲月？", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#7$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歲月會填平絕大多數的鴻溝，也會牢牢地將人綁在一起，無論他們對此作何想法。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們還會是好搭檔，是嗎？", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_103_angel_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我們會一直是好搭檔。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_103_angel_1#9$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，往前走就是了。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會經歷許多事情，她也將經歷許多事情。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許你們各自的故事並無太多相交之處。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，只要你們在某時某刻共用著同一種生活。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，你就無需為此擔憂。", "name": "阿格尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}